item.title: I need help with this
item.dc:creator: @mLexus mLexus
item.description:
@mLexus wrote:

  1. Check the details you have are correct, and the no-ip DUC is online and showing the ip you registered as working.
  2. Check you have port-forwarded correctly in your routerâ€™s configuration website (i.e 192.168.2.1)
  3. Make sure your server is accepting connections and the batch file says it is online.
